::FZ::

"Yes, I would," FZ replies, turning around and walking back to the lab. He watches as the drones finish setting each creature into a test room, then lock the door to that room.

"Now, on to buisness." FZ says to himself, walking out of the room. He taps a few buttons on his wrist watch, accessing the scanners of the Iron Fist.
